column2: age_class <- select(fire_main, Age, Classification) %>% na.exclude %>% filter(Classification == "Career" | Classification == "Volunteer") %>% arrange(Classification)
group_by(fire_main, Classification) %>% summarize(mean_age = mean(as.numeric(Age), na.rm = TRUE), sd_age = sd(as.numeric(Age), na.rm = TRUE), total = n())
